          "type": "text",
          "text": "usp_Validation_GetUtilityContactDiscrepancy",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to identify discrepancies between utility company contacts associated with a specific SBMR (Submission and Billing Management Report) header record. It retrieves records where the utility company associated with the contact address does not match the utility company recorded in the SBMR header. This procedure is useful for validating data consistency between different tables related to utility company information."
        }
